Oceanhorn: Monster of Uncharted Seas combines
captivating storytelling, breathtaking 3D
visuals and exciting gameplay into one epic
action-adventure experience. In the game you
explore the islands of Uncharted Seas, a
world filled with many dangers, puzzles and
secrets. You must fight monsters, learn to
use magic and discover ancient treasures,
which will help you on your quest. Use all
of your wits and skill to unravel the
mysteries of the ancient kingdom of Arcadia
and the sea monster, Oceanhorn.

- 15+ hours of story driven gameplay
- Great controls for both Controller and
Mouse and Keyboard
- Classic gameplay in stunning 3D
